</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[9]">
<![CDATA[水厂出水余氯2,CL_Out_Plant_2,单位:mg/L]]>
</Comment>
<Comment Operand="[10]">
<![CDATA[清水池液位，Level_C-Well,单位:m]]>
</Comment>
